page.title: 11A Day in Keith's Life.
page.content: My mum woke me and I had my breakfast at quarter to eight. I cleaned my teeth and washed before taking Scamp, our dog, for a walk. I caught the bus to school. I arrived at school at quarter to nine for register. We had hymn practice, maths for an hour and then break when we play games or breakdance. After break we did P.E. and drama. At five to twelve we had dinner. I have a packed lunch, most people have school dinners. After dinner we had an another break, then the M4s went swimming at Glossop Road Baths. After swimming we did our topic on lifestyles until home time at twenty five to four. I caught the bus home and took Scamp out. After tea I cycled down to church for choir practice. When I arrived home I practised my trumpet, watched some T.V. and went to bed at nine fifteen.
